<item>
            <title>[LU-1886] Test failure on test suite conf-sanity, subtest test_41b</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1886</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Chris Gearing &amp;lt;chris@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MDS console shows an LBUG.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;19:56:04:LustreError: 166-1: MGC10.10.4.186@tcp: Connection to MGS (at 0@lo) was lost; in progress operations using this service will fail&lt;br/&gt;
19:56:04:Lustre: MGS: Client b8011f6d-946f-08ae-3a76-2fd14e437ca0 (at 0@lo) reconnecting&lt;br/&gt;
19:56:04:LustreError: 31979:0:(obd_class.h:527:obd_set_info_async()) obd_set_info_async: dev 0 no operation&lt;br/&gt;
19:56:04:LustreError: 32318:0:(mgs_internal.h:288:mgs_env_info()) ASSERTION( info != ((void *)0) ) failed: &lt;br/&gt;
19:56:04:LustreError: 32318:0:(mgs_internal.h:288:mgs_env_info()) LBUG&lt;br/&gt;
19:56:04:Pid: 32318, comm: llog_process_th&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e6784022-fbdc-11e1-bde2-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e6784022-fbdc-11e1-bde2-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_41b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test failed to respond and timed out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 41b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
